# The legacy Vite/JSX prototype that used to live here (src/, *.jsx, index.html,
# uploads/, the FRONTEND_* design docs) is kept ON DISK as a design reference but
# is no longer version-controlled. Only the shipped app — frontend/nextjs/ — is
# tracked. This rule ignores everything directly under frontend/ except the real
# app and this file itself, so the legacy files stay untracked going forward.
/*
!/nextjs/
!/.gitignore
